Hash mismatches must be reported to department.
1. ACCESS: Department records are restricted to authorized CS faculty and cleared admin staff only.
2. DATA SECURITY: All sensitive files must remain in the designated Department_Docs directory.
3. CREDENTIALS: Never share system passwords, shadow backup keys, or OTPs with unauthorized personnel.
4. INTEGRITY: Any manual modification of financial or staff records outside the Guardian system is strictly prohibited.
5. INCIDENTS: Suspected unauthorized access or hash mismatches must be reported to the IT Security Team immediately.
